

https://pixinvent.com/demo/vuexy-react-admin-dashboard-template/demo-1/apps/todo . Actually just use that page and link all task to a project, like a project drop down under the add task button. This will save you alot of development time. Click opening a project auto selects that project and opens the task for that project.
Also link these tasks in to the Calendar that came with theme as clickable labels --> https://pixinvent.com/demo/vuexy-react-admin-dashboard-template/demo-1/apps/calendar . Calendar will have its own menu.


